THE NORTHERN IMPERIAL CHINA TOUR - Navyo Nepal Discover Asia

&nbsp; 
 Travelling on the  roof of the world  today is the experience more spectacular than you might imagine, you will feel really "close to heaven"! 
 His endless plateaus and its salt lakes, its perennially snow-capped peaks and ancient monasteries like Sakya, Tashilumpo, or the majestic Potala Palace in Lhasa, blend with the colors of the clouds never still. 
 You discover monasteries, temples, monastic entire cities with their winding lanes. you will enjoy unforgettable views from the train of clouds or meditate in the Rongbuk monastery at the foot of Everest! 
 Visit Tibet with us, it means "living" a journey, an experience that will remain in your heart forever! 
 &nbsp; 
 We are here presenting just some of the possible tour, but  many more chance are available , if you can not find what you want,   write to us   and let us know how can we help you to realize your travel dream!

&nbsp; 
 Attraverso tutto  l'altipiano del Tibet  ci sono numerosi itinerari di&nbsp;  trekking  meravigliosi per chi ama la remotezza, la montagna e la natura. Qui proponiamo alcuni esempi di trekking, da quello breve, leggero e facile fino a quelli pi&ugrave; lunghi e pi&ugrave; impegnativ. 
 Nel Tibet ancora prevale il  trekking con campi tendati , accompagnati da tibetani esperti con i loro cavalli o yak, solo al monte  Kailash  ad oggi &egrave; possibile dormire in  trek lodges  basiche. 
 We are presenting here some of the possibilities, but  much more is possible  to organize, if you can not find here what you want,   write to us   and let us know how can we help you to realize your trekking !

I nostri  viaggi low cost  in  Tibet  hanno un equilibrio ben scelto fra economicit&agrave; e logistica professionale, con sistemazioni adeguate che vi faranno vivere un viaggio stupendo in piena sicurezza.  I viaggi low cost risparmiano nei "lussi" e serve un minimo di spirito di adattamento, con i pernottamenti nelle Guest House per esempio. Possiamo realizzare quasi tutti i nostri viaggi e tour, trekking, outdoor e mountainbike in modalit&agrave; low cost. \r\n &nbsp; \r\n We are presenting here just some of the possibilities, but  much more is possible , if you can not find what you want,   write to us   and let us know how can we help you to realize your travel dream!
